text: Ærest up of Temese, andlang Merfleotes to Pollene stocce.
Swa on Bulinga fenn, of tham fenne æfter thær ealdan dic to Cuforde.
Upp andlang Teoburnan to thære wide herestret, æfter there herestret to thære ealde stoccene sancte Andreas on Holeburne.
Swa innan Lundane fenn, andlang fennes suth on Temese on middan streame.
Andlang streame be lande & be strande eft on Merfleote.
Ærest æt Sandgæte thær tha threo marce togædere gath, west thanon andlang Hemstedes mearce to Mærburnan.
Andlang burnan to Wætlingan stræte, andlang stræte into Bræingte.
Up andlang Brægente innan fihte burnan, of tham burnan to tham wogan æpsan.
Thanon to tham ældan hagtreowe, of tham treowe to tham thrim mærcum æt Sandgate.
Ærest æt Sandgæte, swa east to bedegares swicleage, thær suth to Deormodes wican.
Of Deormodes wican to medeman Hemstede, swa forth &lang hagan to risc leage.
Of risc leage west æfter mærce to tham bæruwe, of tham bærue west andlang mærce to stangrave.
Of tham grave innan Wætlinga stræte, swa north &lang wætlinge stræte to mær burne.
Of mær burnan of east æfter mearce to sandgæte.
